revision.text:
During the Parade of Nations section of the [[1972 Summer Olympics]] opening ceremony, athletes from each country participating in the Olympics paraded into the arena. The Parade of Nations was organised according to the German alphabet, with the first country following Greece being Egypt, while the host, [[West Germany at the 1972 Summer Olympics|West Germany]], entered last.<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRZafGVuR0Q Munich 1972 Opening Ceremony] YouTube</ref> Music during the parade of nations is composed by [[Kurt Edelhagen]].
